  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3457830/extras/1f058b87639f108af1e61819930fdbed.webp?t=1746968140\" width=400 height=30 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >CITYVENTORY is a unique city builder game with a fresh perspective. Unlike traditional city builders, you can freely move and reposition your tiles at any time! However, careful planning is still essential, as any unused tiles are lost when the round ends.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3457830/extras/35bf49afbe2f4ce37321736b680bdbce.poster.avif?t=1746968140\" width=800 height=440 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3457830/extras/35bf49afbe2f4ce37321736b680bdbce.webm?t=1746968140\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3457830/extras/35bf49afbe2f4ce37321736b680bdbce.mp4?t=1746968140\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3457830/extras/e00fcd44513b7349a7d837c57243001c.webp?t=1746968140\" width=400 height=30 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The main objective in CITYVENTORY is to synergize tiles to maximize your score. Some tiles have synergies, offering bonus points when placed together. For example, mills gain additional points for each adjacent farm, and farms also boost each other’s points. However, mills have a negative synergy with other mills, so placing two mills next to each other will cause you to lose points.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3457830/extras/c71da05b81c991be6929a03fb93cd4d8.poster.avif?t=1746968140\" width=800 height=440 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3457830/extras/c71da05b81c991be6929a03fb93cd4d8.webm?t=1746968140\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3457830/extras/c71da05b81c991be6929a03fb93cd4d8.mp4?t=1746968140\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3457830/extras/37f0077f02add4f5312507993bd6e756.webp?t=1746968140\" width=400 height=30 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Once you reach the required points to advance to the next goal, you unlock a new tile type to expand your synergy opportunities. You’ll be able to choose from three available tiles to add to your tile pool and you’ll also receive one guaranteed copy of it. Your choice may depend on the tiles already placed or the terrain features of your city.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3457830/extras/bfd68777a3d18d289ae720069ac520c1.poster.avif?t=1746968140\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3457830/extras/bfd68777a3d18d289ae720069ac520c1.webm?t=1746968140\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3457830/extras/bfd68777a3d18d289ae720069ac520c1.mp4?t=1746968140\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3457830/extras/6c02033eead85d240113249a3d8fb037.webp?t=1746968140\" width=400 height=30 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >When you score enough points to advance to a new stage, you can expand your city, giving you more space to work with. Once your city is fully expanded, continuing to earn points will allow you to unlock larger cities with diverse features and challenges.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3457830/extras/b22b8b4f78dbe7d18913733416a67648.poster.avif?t=1746968140\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3457830/extras/b22b8b4f78dbe7d18913733416a67648.webm?t=1746968140\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3457830/extras/b22b8b4f78dbe7d18913733416a67648.mp4?t=1746968140\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3457830/extras/71e7495979edca82cb2adb275fabdb03.webp?t=1746968140\" width=400 height=30 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >An original mix of city building and inventory management genres</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Rewarding decision making situations</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Variety of tile synergies</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Many unlockable tiles</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Cartoony art style</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >High replay value</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Global Leaderboards</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Great for trying and beating your high score</p></li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3457830/extras/1f058b87639f108af1e61819930fdbed.webp?t=1746968140\" width=400 height=30 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >CITYVENTORY is a unique city builder game with a fresh perspective. Unlike traditional city builders, you can freely move and reposition your tiles at any time! However, careful planning is still essential, as any unused tiles are lost when the round ends.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3457830/extras/35bf49afbe2f4ce37321736b680bdbce.poster.avif?t=1746968140\" width=800 height=440 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3457830/extras/35bf49afbe2f4ce37321736b680bdbce.webm?t=1746968140\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3457830/extras/35bf49afbe2f4ce37321736b680bdbce.mp4?t=1746968140\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3457830/extras/e00fcd44513b7349a7d837c57243001c.webp?t=1746968140\" width=400 height=30 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The main objective in CITYVENTORY is to synergize tiles to maximize your score. Some tiles have synergies, offering bonus points when placed together. For example, mills gain additional points for each adjacent farm, and farms also boost each other’s points. However, mills have a negative synergy with other mills, so placing two mills next to each other will cause you to lose points.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><