/video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3457830/extras/6c02033eead85d240113249a3d8fb037.webp?t=1746968140\" width=400 height=30 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >When you score enough points to advance to a new stage, you can expand your city, giving you more space to work with. Once your city is fully expanded, continuing to earn points will allow you to unlock larger cities with diverse features and challenges.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3457830/extras/b22b8b4f78dbe7d18913733416a67648.poster.avif?t=1746968140\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3457830/extras/b22b8b4f78dbe7d18913733416a67648.webm?t=1746968140\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3457830/extras/b22b8b4f78dbe7d18913733416a67648.mp4?t=1746968140\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3457830/extras/71e7495979edca82cb2adb275fabdb03.webp?t=1746968140\" width=400 height=30 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >An original mix of city building and inventory management genres</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Rewarding decision making situations</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Variety of tile synergies</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Many unlockable tiles</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Cartoony art style</p></li><li><p c